Sige na... huwag kang magalit.

44
00:05:38,940 --> 00:05:41,847
Malalaking tenga at maitim na puwitan, pero
kasintahan ka pa rin ni Erng-Erng.

45
00:05:41,848 --> 00:05:43,848
Ayan, ayan.

46
00:05:46,366 --> 00:05:48,046
Uy, tapos na akong magpakumbaba sa'yo.

47
