150
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:40,066
Sa tingin ko hindi ito tugma sa vibe ng tindahan.

151
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:41,680
Iyon ang iniisip ko.

152
00:15:42,966 --> 00:15:44,133
Sige, tuloy na natin ito.

153
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:46,280
Mayroon ka pa bang ibang gustong baguhin?

154
00:15:46,866 --> 00:15:47,866
Hmm.

155
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:54,765
Sana'y magdahan-dahan lang kayo, Ginoong Erng at Ginoong In.
Gagamit lang ako ng banyo.

156
00:15:54,766 --> 00:15:55,566
Sige.

157
00:15:55,566 --> 00:15:56,566
Sigurado.

158
00:16:08,666 --> 00:16:09,966
Hindi nakasuksok ang damit mo.

159
00:16:10,866 --> 00:16:12,300
Itago mo nang ganito.

160
00:16:12,566 --> 00:16:13,566
Gaya ng ginawa ko.

161
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,400
Hindi pwede.

162
00:16:16,066 --> 00:16:17,706
Hindi komportable ang pakiramdam kapag isinuot ko ito.

163
00:16:21,826 --> 00:16:23,466
Iyon ay dahil hindi mo ginagawa nang tama.

164
00:16:31,866 --> 00:16:32,866
Tulungan mo ako.

165
00:16:39,266 --> 00:16:40,900
Tinutulungan kita isuot 'yan.

166
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,133
Hindi ko kailangan ng tulong. Kaya ko na itong gawin mag-isa.

167
00:16:54,166 --> 00:16:55,246
Ano sa tingin ninyo?

168
00:16:55,959 --> 00:16:57,959
Sabihin mo lang sa akin kung
may gusto kang adjustments.

169
00:16:58,466 --> 00:16:59,466
Nakuha ko.

170
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:26,300
Hindi ko ito kinakain.

171
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,000
Hmph.

172
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,933
Pero inorder ko ito para sa iyo.

173
00:17:32,366 --> 00:17:33,400
Hindi ako kumakain ng matatamis.

174
00:17:38,066 --> 00:17:39,066
Sige, kung ganoon.

175
00:18:06,533 --> 00:18:08,053
Pasensya na, kailangan ko lang gumamit ng banyo.

176
00:18:08,566 --> 00:18:09,566
Sigurado.

177
00:18:17,733 --> 00:18:18,733
Pasensya na.

178
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,200
Sige.

179
00:18:29,666 --> 00:18:30,666
