182
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,300
Sundan mo lang ako.

183
00:18:36,466 --> 00:18:37,866
Malalaman mo rin sa lalong madaling panahon, munting Erng.

184
00:18:41,273 --> 00:18:43,473
Ganito ba talaga tayo papasok nang magkahawak-kamay?

185
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,000
Nakakailang ang pakiramdam?

186
