215
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,200
Talaga, Hija?

216
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:41,500
Teka, teka, teka.

217
00:20:42,266 --> 00:20:43,266
Ikaw.

218
00:20:43,533 --> 00:20:44,566
